<p>SC/ST PoA act, 1989</p>
<p>section <span style="color:#f1c40f">3</span> - intentionally insult with<em> intent to humiliate</em> sc/st in place <em><strong>within public view</strong></em>&nbsp;-</p>
<p style="margin-left:40px">SC 2020 verdict :&nbsp;<em>public view&nbsp;</em>&nbsp;+&nbsp;<em>intent to humiliate </em>are essential</p>
<p style="margin-left:40px"><em>public view =&nbsp;</em>not the presence of relatives + within 4 walls</p>
